@startuml ZMQ_RPC_Metrics_Simple
title ZMQ Metrics (MetaPb + client_id map fallback)

participant Client as "Thread-1\n(Python/C++ Caller)"
participant StubOrUnary as "Thread-1\n(Stub AsyncWrite or Unary SendAll/SendConnMsg)"
participant FrontQ as "ZmqFrontend\nSendMsg + ZmqFrontWorker"
participant Server as "ZmqService I/O\n(FrontendToBackend / reply path)"
participant Worker as "WorkerEntry\n(Business Execute)"
participant Map as "Process map\nclient_id -> ticks"

legend right
|= Color |= Meaning |
|<#C8E6C9> Green|MetaPb path (wall-clock ts on ticks)|
|<#FFF9C4> Yellow|MetaPb main path; may be missing on some branches|
|<#FFCDD2> Red|Use concurrent map by **client_id** (param name in code: traceId)|
endlegend

== Request (two shapes) ==

Client -> StubOrUnary: start RPC

note over StubOrUnary
Async stub path
end note
StubOrUnary -[#2E7D32]> StubOrUnary: RecordTickWithTs(CLIENT_ENQUEUE)
StubOrUnary -[#2E7D32]> Map: save(**client_id**, enqueue)
StubOrUnary -> FrontQ: ZmqFrontend::SendMsg(que)
FrontQ -[#2E7D32]> FrontQ: RecordTickWithTs(CLIENT_TO_STUB)
FrontQ -[#2E7D32]> Map: update(client_id, to_stub)
FrontQ -[#2E7D32]> FrontQ: RouteToZmq*/Unix: RecordTickWithTs(CLIENT_SEND)\n(before meta serialize & send)
FrontQ -[#2E7D32]> Map: update(client_id, send)
FrontQ -[#2E7D32]> Server: on wire (MetaPb + payload)

note over StubOrUnary
Unary path (common in smoke)
end note
StubOrUnary -[#2E7D32]> StubOrUnary: StartTheClock; RecordTickWithTs(CLIENT_ENQUEUE)
StubOrUnary -[#2E7D32]> Map: save(client_id, enqueue)
StubOrUnary -[#2E7D32]> StubOrUnary: SendConnMsg: TO_STUB + SEND 同线程连续打点
StubOrUnary -[#2E7D32]> Map: update to_stub, send
StubOrUnary -> FrontQ: mQue_->SendMsg
FrontQ -[#2E7D32]> Server: 同上（若经 Gateway 再发仍走 Route* 的 CLIENT_SEND）

== Server ==

Server -[#2E7D32]> Server: RecordTick(SERVER_RECV)\n(FrontendToBackend 解析后)
Server -[#2E7D32]> Worker: dispatch
Worker -[#2E7D32]> Worker: RecordTick(SERVER_DEQUEUE)
Worker -[#2E7D32]> Worker: business
Worker -[#2E7D32]> Worker: RecordTick(SERVER_EXEC_END)
Worker -[#2E7D32]> Worker: append tick **SERVER_EXEC_NS** (ts=**handler duration ns**, 非墙钟)
Worker -[#2E7D32]> Map: (无, 仅 meta)
Server -[#43A047]> Server: ServiceToClient: **SERVER_SEND**.ts=墙钟 now;\nreply 指标=now - **SERVER_EXEC_END**
Server -[#43A047]--> FrontQ: response MetaPb (ticks 含 SERVER_SEND)

note right of Worker
**SERVER_EXEC_NS** 与前后 tick 的 **ts 差** 无意义，\n不得用于 RecordTick lap；\n客户端分解 network 时读 duration 或 DEQUEUE/EXEC_END 墙钟差
end note

== Response ==

FrontQ -[#2E7D32]> StubOrUnary: receive queue -> AsyncRead / ReadAll
StubOrUnary -[#2E7D32]> StubOrUnary: RecordTick(CLIENT_RECV)
StubOrUnary -[#2E7D32]> StubOrUnary: **Log [ZmqTickOrder]** 打全链；再算 7 指标
StubOrUnary -[#F9A825]> StubOrUnary: 若 meta 缺 CLIENT_*, 用 Map(**client_id**) 回退

note over StubOrUnary, Map
回包后 grep 日志: **[ZmqTickOrder]**\n见 README 验收步骤
end note

note over StubOrUnary
7 个指标:
client_queuing, client_stub_send,
server_queue_wait, server_exec, server_reply,
rpc_e2e, rpc_network
end note

@enduml
